data.description: This house has so many options.  Located near bike trail, the boat launch and Alleghany river the opportunities are endless.  Recently remodeled which includes new windows, kitchens, and bathrooms.  This home is currently setup as an up/down duplex but can easily be used as a single family home. The first floor has an open floor plan with first floor laundry, one bedroom and one bathroom.  The second floor has an eat in kitchen. one bedroom and one bathroom.  Schedule your showing today, you don't want to miss this one.
